videos.description: V.J. King comes up with the steal and rises up to stuff a dunk right in the defender's face.
videos.headline: King mashes dunk over defender

videos.description: Markus Howard finds a wide-open Ed Morrow diving to the basket and he throws down a strong one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Morrow throws down one-handed slam

videos.description: Markus Howard throws a dime to a rolling Theo John who throws down a big two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Howard drops a dime to John for two-handed jam
